@rothardo good question, let me ask

@matthiasblaesing @lkishalmi @ebarboni  what do you think, should we rename everything?

I believe in this case, where Hudson was discontinued and lives on as Jenkins and we have several releases on maven central with modules which support Hudson (and Jenkins incidentally), we should simply rename everything.

Since copy + deprecate doesn't make a lot of sense here. It would create just a bunch of dead modules (which support dead software) in the repo which have to be built and tested.

